<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />In you, Yahweh, I take refuge;</para>

<para style="q1">let me never be put to shame.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Rescue me and make me safe in your righteousness;</para>

<para style="q1">turn your ear to me and save me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Be to me a rock for refuge where I may always go;</para>

<para style="q1">you have given a command to save me,</para>

<para style="q1">for you are my rock and my fortress.</para>
